title: Hour 3 - The Goose Got Loose, Cris Collinsworth
itunes:title: Hour 3 - The Goose Got Loose, Cris Collinsworth
description:
Dan reacts to the goose that camped out at Dodgers Stadium during last night's NLDS between the Dodgers and Padres. And he chats with SNF Analyst Cris Collinsworth about tonight's NFL game and the rest of the NFL.
